    <item>
      <title>美国两年期国债收益率攀升逾 5% 至 11 月以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/us-two-year-yield-climbs-past-5-to-highest-level-since-november</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，近期数据显示通胀在实现央行 2% 目标方面缺乏进一步进展，美国两年期国债收益率升至 5% 以上，达到 11 月以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/us-two-year-yield-climbs-past-5-to-highest-level-since-november</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 17:36:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国称新市场规则不会导致大规模退市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/china-says-new-market-rules-won-t-lead-to-massive-delistings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在小盘股暴跌后，中国最高证券监管机构试图减轻投资者对新证券交易所规则的担忧，称他们预计这些变化不会导致退市数量激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/china-says-new-market-rules-won-t-lead-to-massive-delistings</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 17:32:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
